fontconfig dependency package
=============================

Target: @TARGET_TRIPLE@
Target kind: @TARGET_KIND@

Components:
- expat from python_dependencies base prefix
- FreeType @FREETYPE_VERSION@
- fontconfig @FONTCONFIG_VERSION@

Build tools:
- GNU gperf @GPERF_VERSION@, built for the build machine only

The package is intended as a small dynamic dependency prefix for OpenJDK
builds.  It ships headers, pkg-config files, shared libraries, and fontconfig
configuration data.  Command-line fontconfig tools are intentionally not built
because this package is consumed as a cross-built dependency prefix.
